{
  "stem": "10699.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were bothering us and the lice were bothering us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were hungry, starving and yet we were beaten all the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had the impression that they had mostly criminals there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Kramer was now the chief of-- the kommando of Bergen-Belsen and he gave us the same treatment as Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, on the 2nd-- on the 2nd of February or something like that-- end of February-- we were again-- there was a big selection and this time, again, a group was chosen for transport.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was amongst the 500 or 700 that were chosen and-- and Janine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Every time we tried to keep together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Her sister, now, we didn't know what happened to her sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was the other girl called Susanne was with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When we arrived in Raguhn, which is, I understand near Dresden, we were taken-- we were taken to barracks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the guards at the time, when they saw our pitiful state, they said-- well, a little bit kinder with us, and they were a    bit nicer, and I think they gave us a little bit of food.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we thought that it was paradise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It didn't last very long because Kramer came as a commandant, and [INAUDIBLE] he came with his guards.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So that was finished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same-- the same",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "conditions.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were sent-- we were going to that factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- they manufactured-- they manufactured pieces for airplanes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- Janine and I were given the job-- what would I call it?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sol-- Soldering?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Soldering?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or something-- Cutting out, soldering, things like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were working mostly sometimes at daytime, sometimes nighttime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The conditions were very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By that time, we had such diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on top of it, no food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one fat German who passed us once, he says, tomorrow I bring you-- tomorrow I'll bring you food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said we were already dreaming of getting food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the next day when we arrived, we opened that little drawer to look what he brought us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had brought us potato peels.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we knew that, if we eat potato peels, our diarrhea would get worse.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So of course, we-- we didn't eat it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, people that were with us, like [INAUDIBLE], who is also a survivor and lives in Paris and is trying to make a film about her story, she was also with us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was only 15 and she was very short.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was working on a piece of metal that was so big that you hardly saw her head.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just her head you saw, and she was trying to turn with other girls that big wheel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some were just making tools.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Germans saw exactly the way we looked, the way we were-- were starving, the way we were full of lice, and we were sick, and everything.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I don't remember that one person gave us any food or anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But what I would like to tell you is something else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When we came down from Ber-- from Bergen-Belsen into the station of Raguhn, we had to walk through the town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we could smell the smell of fresh bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were so hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the water was coming out of our mouth, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were so hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were dirty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We must have been dirty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "As we walked through the town, the only thing I can remember was somebody spitting at us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was no pity.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were spitting at us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I couldn't believe that human beings, you know, seeing young girls in such a state could not have any pity, but just spit on us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took us to that camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought in the beginning, it was-- we thought it was  a paradise compared to the others.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It didn't only last a few days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I-- before I was chosen for work, I will never forget that woman, that guard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She said, I managed because I was outside to have colorings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I was working outside-- outdoors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I seemed to have colors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was always chosen for work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because you looked healthy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Healthier.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I had more-- Yeah, colors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, this one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the SS-- the other SS-- says, don't take this one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She's-- she's like a rosy apple completely rotten inside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what-- I said, you, if I could find you again after the war, do you know what I would do to you?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's what she said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But she did send me to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had a lot of bombardments, you see, at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was near Dresden, we could hear it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were quite a bit in shelters.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
